column16: Ryan Braun singles on a ground ball to center fielder Shane Victorino.    Corey Hart to 2nd.

Joe Inglett called out on strikes.

Alcides Escobar singles on a line drive to center fielder Shane Victorino.    Lorenzo Cain to 2nd.
Orlando Hudson grounds out, shortstop Wilson Valdez to first baseman Ryan Howard.    Nick Punto scores.    Denard Span to 3rd.
Denard Span singles on a line drive to center fielder Shane Victorino.    Delmon Young to 3rd.    Nick Punto to 2nd.
Danny Valencia pops out to catcher Brian Schneider in foul territory.
